Luther MARTIN v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 3279. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Dec. 28, 1945. Laynie W. Harrod, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellant. John Brett, Asst. U. S. Atty., of Oklahoma City, Old., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Docketed and dismissed on motion of ap-pellee and stipulation of the parties.
